## mmkit code map

| Concern | Module |
|---------|--------|
| Request term + `X` send | `@mmkit/shared` `buildIpcMessage`, `lengthPrefix` |
| Response parse | `tcpFraming.ts` `tryParseTcpLengthFrame` |
| Method payloads | `cbIpcCatalog.ts` |
| Frame build per command | `CBServerConnectionContext.buildIpcFrame` |
| TCP socket I/O | `CBConnectionPort.ts` |
| Answer dispatch | `cbreader/CBConnectionReaderContext.ts` |
| Command API | `CBServerConnectionActor.ts` / `CBConnectionHandle.ts` |
| IPC method enum | `cbIpcCatalog.ts` `CB_IPC_METHODS` |
| Mock TCP tests | `test/cbserver/mockTcpSocket.ts` — uses `formatTcpLengthFrame` for fake answers |

**Reader/writer split:** writer sends `lengthPrefix`; reader **only** uses `tryParseTcpLengthFrame` (not `lengthPrefix`).

