## Quick hex example

Request body (before `X` header):

```
ipcmessage("","",ENROLL_ME,["mmkit","user@host_x64_linux"]).\n
```

If body length = 58 (0x3A):

```
58 03A 00 00 00  →  X 00 00 00 3A  +  body bytes
```

Response:

```
45\n
ipcanswer("cbserver",ok,"my-client-id").\n
```

where `45` = character length of `ipcanswer("cbserver",ok,"my-client-id").`
